---
title: Lemon Ricotta Pancakes with Crème Fraîche plus Cherry Maple Syrup & a Spinach Orange Salad
description: Over here, we think brunch is a food group—and a really important and scrumptious one. Today’s fix: decadent lemon ricotta pancakes and a dollop of zesty crème fraîche. Ready to take it to the next level? You’ll drizzle cherry maple syrup and sprinkle crunchy walnuts all over. Next, you’ll serve up a lovely spinach salad with oranges and creamy feta on the side. Feel free to break out the special plates or just enjoy this meal in your PJs.
